function state() {
 eth.getCode(sender, "0x0")
 eth.getBalance(sender, "0x0")
 eth.getTransactionCount(sender, "0x0")
}

var txHash;

function sendTx() {
  eth.estimateGas({
  "from": sender,
  "gas": "0x6691b7",
  "gasPrice": "0x4a817c800",
  "data": ""
  });

  txHash = eth.sendRawTransaction("");
}

var receipt;
var tx;

function getReceipt() {
	receipt = eth.getTransactionReceipt(txHash);
}

var contract = {};

function check() {
  contract.Code = eth.getCode(receipt.contractAddress,"0x0");
  contract.Balance = eth.getBalance(receipt.contractAddress,"0x0");
  tx = eth.getTransactionByHash(txHash)
}
